channel.title: Digibbo Server (Habbo Retro) Release!
channel.description:
It's The release of the Habbo Retro "Digibbo"
We do belive it has the new items like trax etc but we have not figured them out. Go to this site: digibbo.ulmb.com
and follow the tutorial there. If you have hamachi and know how to use it do not follow just Go to this network.
Network name: Digibbo Network name: Digibbo1 Network name: Digibbo2 Network name: Digibbo3 Network name: Digibbo4 Pass: 123 and then log onto the Version 1 on the front page!
